    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Validation results demonstrate NIH prediction within 15% of experimental measurements across all five operating points. The RH index is below 1.0 for all COU conditions, supporting the regulatory submission decision.",
